headline: Zumiez Q4 Earnings & Sales Miss Estimates, Comps Increase Y/Y
summary: ZUMZ's fiscal fourth-quarter results reflect lower y/y sales. However, the gross margin expands 190 bps y/y to 36.2%.

headline: Guess & WHP Global Partner With Signal Brands to Expand rag & bone
summary: GES and WHP Global team up with Signal Brands to expand rag & bone's handbags and leather goods, leveraging Signal Brands' expertise in accessories and global reach.
